  "body": "### Describe the bug\r\n\r\nThe documentation for `hibernate-orm` (https://quarkus.io/guides/hibernate-orm) lists 3 configuration properties that cannot be set together when using `application.yaml`.\r\n\r\n```\r\nquarkus.hibernate-orm.database.generation (string)\r\nquarkus.hibernate-orm.database.generation.create-schemas (boolean)\r\nquarkus.hibernate-orm.database.generation.halt-on-error (boolean)\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhen writing the YAML, in order to set all 3 properties, this would require `quarkus.hibernate-orm.database.generation` to be both a string and object.\r\n\r\n### Output of `java -version`\r\n\r\nOpenJDK 11.0.11\r\n\r\n### Quarkus version or git rev\r\n\r\nQuarkus 2.4.1\r\n\r\n### Build tool (ie. output of `mvnw --version` or `gradlew --version`)\r\n\r\nGradle 7.2",
